  <brief_title>The Depth of Endotracheal Tube Insertion</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Depth of Endotracheal Tube Insertion - Use of Direct Laryngoscopy and Videolaryngoscopy (GlideScope), Comparison of Methods</official_title>
